$title: Battle Flag T-Shirt
$description:
Step off the ice with confidence and style with Titan Battlegear's line of hockey T-shirts, crafted for those who live and breathe the sport. These tees are a salute to the relentless spirit and passion that define hockey culture.

Bold Design: Each shirt in our collection features a unique, hockey-themed graphic that embodies the ruggedness and spirit of the game. From iconic symbols of the sport to designs that speak to the heart of a hockey player, these graphics are all about making a statement. Whether it’s the power play or the penalty kill, these designs resonate with every facet of hockey life.

Back Detail: Showcasing the Titan Battlegear logo just below the neck, each shirt carries the mark of quality and dedication to hockey excellence. This logo is more than just a brand identifier; it's a symbol of your commitment to the game and being part of a community that respects and loves the sport.

Sleeve Emblem: Adorning the sleeve of each shirt is a distinctive Titan Battlegear emblem. This detail not only adds to the aesthetic appeal of the shirt but also serves as a badge of pride for those who wear it. It’s a tribute to your dedication to the game and a brand that stands for the highest standards in the hockey world.

Premium Fabric and Athletic Fit: Constructed with high-quality materials, our T-shirts are built to last through every face-off and goal celebration. $title: BG 2.0 LS - BOSTON STRONG
$description:
Designed for the player who leads with both skill and swagger, Titan’s BattleGear 2.0 delivers superior cut resistance, maximum coverage, and unparalleled comfort. 

This shirt features A7-A9 cut-resistant neck, collar, and wrist protection, thanks to TITANOTEX™, our proprietary fabric engineered in North Carolina. The patent-pending Arc~Guard™ collar provides maximum coverage of critical areas, while the contoured shape ensures it’s the most comfortable fit you’ll find, powered by the patent-pending Stretch ProCurve™ technology. It’s the ultimate game-changer—eliminating Velcro and dynamically stretching and contracting to provide the perfect, protective fit throughout the game.

Built for performance, the athletic fit, 4-way stretch, and quick-dry technology deliver comfort and agility throughout the game. With thermo-regulation and breathable mesh panels, this shirt keeps you cool under pressure while its anti-bacterial fabric keeps you fresh.

Titan’s BattleGear 2.0 Shirt is the safest, most comfortable, and highest-performing shirt in hockey.

Specifications:

  • Body & Sleeve: 87% Polyester, 13% Lycra, 4.16 oz

$title: BG 2.0 LS NECK GUARD SHIRT - EARLY RISER
$description:
Designed for the player who leads with both skill and swagger, Titan’s BattleGear 2.0 delivers superior cut resistance, maximum coverage, and unparalleled comfort. 

This shirt features A7-A9 cut-resistant neck, collar, and wrist protection, thanks to TITANOTEX™, our proprietary fabric engineered in North Carolina. The patent-pending Arc~Guard™ collar provides maximum coverage of critical areas, while the contoured shape ensures it’s the most comfortable fit you’ll find, powered by the patent-pending Stretch ProCurve™ technology. It’s the ultimate game-changer—eliminating Velcro and dynamically stretching and contracting to provide the perfect, protective fit throughout the game.

Built for performance, the athletic fit, 4-way stretch, and quick-dry technology deliver comfort and agility throughout the game. With thermo-regulation and breathable mesh panels, this shirt keeps you cool under pressure while its anti-bacterial fabric keeps you fresh.

Titan’s BattleGear 2.0 Shirt is the safest, most comfortable, and highest-performing shirt in hockey.

Specifications:

  • Body & Sleeve: 87% Polyester, 13% Lycra, 4.16 oz

  • Back Mesh: 90% Polyester, 10% Lycra, 3.24 oz

  • Fit: Fitted Athletic Fit

  • Features:

    • TITANOTEX™ Cut-Resistant Protection

    • ARC~GUARD™ Contoured Collar

    • 4-Way Stretch & Quick Dry

    • Thermo-Regulated & Mesh Panels

    • Anti-Bacterial & Oeko-Tex Certified

Built for those who demand the best—Titan BattleGear.

This shirt features A7-A9 cut-resistant neck, collar, and wrist protection, thanks to TITANOTEX™, our proprietary fabric engineered in North Carolina. Titan’s BattleGear 2.0 Shirt is the safest, most comfortable, and highest-performing shirt in hockey.

$title: BG 2.0 LS NECK GUARD SHIRT - WHITE
$description:
Designed for the player who leads with both skill and swagger, Titan’s BattleGear 2.0 delivers superior cut resistance, maximum coverage, and unparalleled comfort. 

This shirt features A7-A9 cut-resistant neck, collar, and wrist protection, thanks to TITANOTEX™, our proprietary fabric engineered in North Carolina. The patent-pending Arc~Guard™ collar provides maximum coverage of critical areas, while the contoured shape ensures it’s the most comfortable fit you’ll find, powered by the patent-pending Stretch ProCurve™ technology. It’s the ultimate game-changer—eliminating Velcro and dynamically stretching and contracting to provide the perfect, protective fit throughout the game.

Built for performance, the athletic fit, 4-way stretch, and quick-dry technology deliver comfort and agility throughout the game. With thermo-regulation and breathable mesh panels, this shirt keeps you cool under pressure while its anti-bacterial fabric keeps you fresh.

Titan’s BattleGear 2.0 Shirt is the safest, most comfortable, and highest-performing shirt in hockey.

Specifications:

  • Body & Sleeve: 87% Polyester, 13% Lycra, 4.16 oz

  • Back Mesh: 90% Polyester, 10% Lycra, 3.24 oz

  • Fit: Fitted Athletic Fit

  • Features:

    • TITANOTEX™ Cut-Resistant Protection

    • ARC~GUARD™ Contoured Collar

    • 4-Way Stretch & Quick Dry

    • Thermo-Regulated & Mesh Panels

    • Anti-Bacterial & Oeko-Tex Certified

Built for those who demand the best—Titan BattleGear.
categories: arcguard,  Battlegear,  Compression,  cut-resistant,  hockey neck guard shirt,  inline,  spo-cs-disabled,  spo-default,  spo-disabled,  spo-notify-me-enabled

$title: GIVE THE GIFT OF PERFORMANCE AND PROTECTION!
$description:
Looking for the perfect gift for the hockey enthusiast in your life? The Titan BattleGear Gift Cards are a great way to surprise them. Available in $50, $100, $150, and $200, these cards provide the freedom to choose from our innovative product lineup crafted with superior quality and unmatched protection.

Why Choose a Titan Gift Card?
  • Total Flexibility: Let your loved one pick exactly what they need, from our growing range of products.
  • Instant Virtual Delivery: Perfect for any occasion, whether you’re planning ahead or need a last-minute gift.
How It Works:
  1. Choose the gift card amount that best suits your budget.
  2. Complete your purchase and receive the virtual gift card instantly via email.
  3. Share the gift card directly with your loved one or print it out for a personal touch.

$title: MADE FOR BULK
$description:
Designed for the player who leads with both skill and swagger, Titan’s BattleGear 2.0 delivers superior cut resistance, maximum coverage, and unparalleled comfort. 

This shirt features A7-A9 cut-resistant neck, collar, and wrist protection, thanks to TITANOTEX™, our proprietary fabric engineered in North Carolina. The patent-pending Arc~Guard™ collar provides maximum coverage of critical areas, while the contoured shape ensures it’s the most comfortable fit you’ll find, powered by the patent-pending Stretch ProCurve™ technology. It’s the ultimate game-changer—eliminating Velcro and dynamically stretching and contracting to provide the perfect, protective fit throughout the game.

Built for performance, the athletic fit, 4-way stretch, and quick-dry technology deliver comfort and agility throughout the game. With thermo-regulation and breathable mesh panels, this shirt keeps you cool under pressure while its anti-bacterial fabric keeps you fresh.

Titan’s BattleGear 2.0 Shirt is the safest, most comfortable, and highest-performing shirt in hockey.

Specifications:

  • Body & Sleeve: 87% Polyester, 13% Lycra, 4.16 oz

  • Back Mesh: 90% Polyester, 10% Lycra, 3.24 oz

  • Fit: Fitted Athletic Fit

  • Features:

    • TITANOTEX™ Cut-Resistant Protection

    • ARC~GUARD™ Contoured Collar

    • 4-Way Stretch & Quick Dry

    • Thermo-Regulated & Mesh Panels

    • Anti-Bacterial & Oeko-Tex Certified

Built for those who demand the best—Titan BattleGear.

$title: Puck Stops Here T-Shirt
$description: Step off the ice with confidence and style with Titan Battlegear's line of hockey T-shirts, crafted for those who live and breathe the sport. These tees are a salute to the relentless spirit and passion that define hockey culture.<br data-mce-fragment="1"><br data-mce-fragment="1">Bold Design: Each shirt in our collection features a unique, hockey-themed graphic that embodies the ruggedness and spirit of the game. Whether it’s the power play or the penalty kill, these designs resonate with every facet of hockey life.<br data-mce-fragment="1"><br data-mce-fragment="1">Back Detail: Showcasing the Titan Battlegear logo just below the neck, each shirt carries the mark of quality and dedication to hockey excellence. It’s a tribute to your dedication to the game and a brand that stands for the highest standards in the hockey world.<br data-mce-fragment="1"><br data-mce-fragment="1">Premium Fabric and Athletic Fit: Constructed with high-quality materials, our T-shirts are built to last through every faceoff and goal celebration. The fabric is both rugged and comfortable, perfect for enduring the demands of an active lifestyle. The fit is tailored for hockey enthusiasts, offering both comfort and a flattering look.<br data-mce-fragment="1"><br data-mce-fragment="1">Versatile and Stylish: Ideal for wearing to the rink, during casual puck sessions, or as a daily show of your hockey allegiance, these T-shirts are as versatile as they are fashionable. They're designed to carry your passion for hockey into every aspect of your life, from the locker room to your everyday routine.<br data-mce-fragment="1"><br data-mce-fragment="1">Titan Battlegear Hockey T-Shirts are more than just clothing; they're a declaration of your passion for hockey. They symbolize the energy, excitement, and camaraderie of the sport. Wear them with pride and join a community that shares your enthusiasm for the game.

$title: The Hand Grenade
$description:
Hockey warriors, gear up and get ready to dive into the battle on ice with your newest ally – "The Hand Grenade" water bottle. When the game heats up and the ice becomes your battlefield, you need more than just skill and strategy; you need the ultimate hydration grenade in your arsenal.

The Hand Grenade is not your regular water jug; it's your secret weapon. As you charge through each period, The Hand Grenade is there to ensure you stay loaded with hydration power. It's tough as the boards, flexible as a breakaway, and as indispensable as your stick in a power play.

So, lace up, face off, and keep your Hand Grenade close. When the going gets tough, pull the pin on dehydration and get back in the fight with a bottle built for hockey’s toughest warriors. Stay frosty and fueled, team – The Hand Grenade's got your back!

Key Features:

  • 750ml (25oz) bottle: Keeps you hydrated until the very end!

  • 100% Medical Grade Silicone: Crafted from top-quality medical grade silicone, The Hand Grenade ensures your hydration is always safe and pure. This premium material is completely BPA-free, non-toxic, and hypoallergenic, making it perfect for athletes who take their health seriously.

  • Durability Redefined: Virtually indestructible, this bottle can withstand extreme conditions. Drive over it, freeze it, heat it – The Hand Grenade will retain its shape and functionality. It's designed to endure thousands of dishwasher cycles, ensuring it remains a reliable part of your gear for years.

  • Revolutionary Squirt Top Cap: The Hand Grenade boasts the best squirt top cap on the market. This innovative design allows for easy hydration, whether you're on the sidelines or in the thick of the game. The cap’s engineering makes it a breeze to hydrate with or without a helmet, providing a quick, spill-free drink every time.

Benefits of Medical Grade Silicone:

  1. Health-Safe: Free from harmful chemicals, ensuring your drinks stay uncontaminated.
  2. Temperature Resistant: Handles extreme temperatures – both hot and cold – without degrading.
  3. Flexible Yet Tough: Its flexibility doesn’t compromise on toughness; it’s made to last.
  4. Odor and Stain Resistant: Resists odors and stains, keeping your bottle fresh after every wash.
  5. Eco-Friendly: A sustainable option that reduces single-use plastic waste.

"The Hand Grenade" is more than just a water bottle – it's a statement of resilience, innovation, and uncompromising quality. Designed for those who push the limits, it's your new ally in staying hydrated and focused, no matter the challenge. Get ready to elevate your game with The Hand Grenade – the last water bottle you'll ever need.
categories: battle bottle,  hand grenade,  spo-cs-disabled,  spo-default,  spo-disabled,  spo-notify-me-enabled,  water bottle
